{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"PositionError","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPositionError","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation_API\">Geolocation API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPositionError\"><code>GeolocationPositionError</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPositionError/code\"><code>code</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPositionError/message\"><code>message</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Geolocation API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation\"><code>Geolocation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates\"><code>GeolocationCoordinates</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPosition\"><code>GeolocationPosition</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator/geolocation\"><code>Navigator.geolocation</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><strong><code>PositionError</code></strong> 接口表示当定位设备位置时发生错误的原因。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em><code>PositionError</code> 接口没有继承任何属性。</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"positionerror.code_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPositionError/code\"><code>PositionError.code</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回无符号的、简短的错误码。下列值是可能的：\n <table>\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <th scope=\"col\">值</th>\n    <th scope=\"col\">相关联的常量</th>\n    <th scope=\"col\">描述</th>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>1</code></td>\n    <td><code>PERMISSION_DENIED</code></td>\n    <td>地理位置信息的获取失败，因为该页面没有获取地理位置信息的权限。</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>2</code></td>\n    <td><code>POSITION_UNAVAILABLE</code></td>\n    <td>\n     <p>地理位置获取失败，因为至少有一个内部位置源返回一个内部错误。</p>\n    </td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>3</code></td>\n    <td><code>TIMEOUT</code></td>\n    <td>\n     <p>获取地理位置超时，通过定义<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Geolocation/getCurrentPosition_058087067b28ad25fff974fd59827fb6\"><code>PositionOptions.timeout</code></a> 来设置获取地理位置的超时时长。</p>\n    </td>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n </dd>\n <dt id=\"positionerror.message_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPositionError/message\"><code>PositionError.message</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回一个开发者可以理解的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> 来描述错误的详细信息。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em><em><code>PositionError</code> 接口没有实现也没有<em>继承任何方法。</em></em></em></p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"标准","id":"标准","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/geolocation-api/#position_error_interface","title":"Geolocation API"}],"query":"api.GeolocationPositionError"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.GeolocationPositionError","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPositionError/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"请参见","title":"请参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Geolocation_API\" title=\"/en-US/docs/WebAPI/Using_geolocation\">Using geolocation</a></li>\n <li>The <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation\"><code>Geolocation</code></a> interface that use it.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"标准","id":"标准"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"请参见","id":"请参见"}],"summary":"PositionError 接口表示当定位设备位置时发生错误的原因。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GeolocationPositionError","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"GeolocationPositionError","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"GeolocationPositionError","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"PositionError","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"PositionError","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"PositionError","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/geolocationpositionerror","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/geolocationpositionerror/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPositionError","title":"PositionError"}],"pageTitle":"PositionError - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}